issue.title: zsh: command not found: cobra on mac after installation
issue.body:
I have run `go install github.com/spf13/cobra-cli@latest` but cobra still not recognized on terminal.
How can I resolve this?

comment.body:
I uninstalled the go installation from my laptop (mac m1) , I installed fresh one and ran the following 

- export GOPATH=$(go env GOPATH)
- export GOBIN=$GOPATH/bin
- export PATH=$PATH:$GOBIN

that worked for me üëç
